        <p class="lead fw-bold">1. NOTICE</p>
        <p class="mb-sm-5 mb-grid-gutter">This Privacy Policy applies to properties owned and operated by The Nepoz Group Pty Ltd t/a Studify, (“Studify”, “We”, “Us”, “Our”), which include www.studify.au, (“Web Site”) and our mobile app (the "App") (collectively, “Properties”). This Privacy Policy (“Policy”) describes how Studify collects and uses the personal information you provide through our Properties. It also describes the choices available to you regarding our use of personal information about you and how you can access and update this information.</p>
        <p class="mb-sm-5 mb-grid-gutter">Please note that Studify is registered organization based in the AUSTRALIA. Any personal information you provide or we collect is transmitted to, and stored in, the AUSTRALIA, and will also be shared with our recruiting agents, member Colleges and Universities, at your direction, including in countries where laws may be less protective of personal information about you than in your home country.</p>

        <p class="lead fw-bold">2. This policy will let you know about:</p>
