        <p class="mb-sm-5 mb-grid-gutter">Please read carefully this Policy before providing us with any information. This Policy only addresses Studify's privacy practices concerning information collected from our Properties. This Policy also does not cover the privacy or information practices of those web sites that may be linked to or referenced by the Properties or the information practices of Colleges and Universities.</p>
        
        <p class="lead fw-bold">3. Changes to this Policy</p>
        <p class="mb-sm-5 mb-grid-gutter">Changes to this Policy will be posted on this page. We reserve the right to modify this Policy at any time, so please review it periodically to learn of updates.</p>
        
        <p class="lead fw-bold">4. Data Rights and Control</p>
        <p class="mb-sm-5 mb-grid-gutter">Users (defined below) retain ownership of and an interest in all data (including Personal Information) provided to the Properties. However, Studify has the right to use all data provided to the Properties (including Personal Information) in accordance with its Terms of Use and this Privacy Policy. Once a user decides to share Personal Information with a member College or University through the Properties, the member controls that Personal Information and can use it in accordance with its own privacy policy and applicable laws.</p>

